{
  "stem": "3022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The KL was supposed to be tattooed on the forehead.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he told us that unless we produced a certain amount of, of valuables, jewelry, and gold, this is what's going to be done.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we, we collected-- the authorities in the camp collected whatever, whatever they could, but that wasn't enough for him.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we were pulling out the gold from teeth of living people, and we gave him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he was caught in Argentina, extradited to Germany, he was caught with several bags of jewelry, and gold from teeth.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'm sure the gold for many of my friends' teeth was among the things that he was caught with.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Let, let, let me explain to you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Up till that time, the supervision of the camp, the security of the camp, was maintained by the [NON-ENGLISH] and by the internal [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Germans made sure that the Jews watched them-- watched each other, because they instituted what was known as group responsibility.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If a Jew ran away from a detail, work detail, 10 to 20 people from the work detail would be executed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If you ran away from a barracks, from his barrack, the, the people who lived with him in that barrack.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "If he ran away from the camp and he had family, there would be the first one.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So everybody was watching each other.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'll tell you a little story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- when the barracks were being built, a group of my friends and I, approximately the same age, we decided that we wanted to live in one room.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we moved in the barrack, barrack number four.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And most of us were the same age.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We kept the room very clean, very neat.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
